name: AdultDepressionMedications
title: Adult Depression Medications
purpose: (Clinical Focus: The purpose of this value set is to represent medications used to treat depression in the adult population.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use a model element related to Medication.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes concepts for medications used for treatment and management of depression in adults.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes concepts that represent medications that are not recommended for children and adolescents and are solely used in the adult population.)
